Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿迪斯舰长
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,队长在哪呢 内部到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.60,0:14:47.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,父亲的克隆吗 谁会相信这种童话故事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不想相信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很遗憾 这是事实
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.39,0:14:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dominion来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距离50 Green Bravo
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全员一级战备
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.13,0:15:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有3个热源接近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.94,0:15:04.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比对热纹 是那三架机体
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的门就要打开了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.01,0:15:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由我开启
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后这个世界就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:17.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个无尽欲望的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.96,0:15:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那些垂死挣扎 自以为是的愚者将如愿以偿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.85,0:15:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,基拉!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.88,0:15:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们保护战舰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注意Nazca级的动向
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gottfried 瞄准 装填Korinthos
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.14,0:15:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主炮准备
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.44,0:16:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反光束爆雷发射 击毁他们的母舰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:08.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们能干得了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人能阻止得了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这覆盖宇宙的憎恨的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.01,0:16:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 只有一架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那这次就快点解决吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gottfried 发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回避
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,导弹四枚 Green Alpha
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左转舵10
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.04,0:16:48.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伊扎克 能听见吗 要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.41,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得不是ZAFT的就是敌人 那就开枪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.24,0:16:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是谁被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.86,0:17:04.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还不清楚 但我要走了
